{"tid":316860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烈日下送別遼寧號　市民為解放軍撐傘","createTime":"2017-07-11T05:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T13:48:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67a829bdea41f286b8aad0cdb185e822fd541480","tid":316860,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170711/s00001/df11a9ffc993e9e566936a7c6502959a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2Fdf11a9ffc993e9e566936a7c6502959a.jpg&h=57e44d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國首艘航空母艦「遼寧號」及3艘屬艦完成5日訪港行程，昂船洲軍營今早舉行歡送儀式，60名來自旅港開平商會的小學生都有份參加，老師細心地為同學準備了退熱貼，以防中暑。<br />\n<br />\n在歡送儀式上，解放軍海軍副司令員丁魏向傳媒表示，「感謝香港人民，祝願香港繁榮穩定。」<br />\n<br />\n逾百名市民出席歡送儀式，包括約60名來自旅港開平商會的小學生，另有逾50名九龍社團聯會及八鄉鄉事委員會的成員。<br />\n<br />\n前來參加儀式小學生在老師陪同下於9時半到場。10歲的甄璟堯說「好開心」，但感到「超熱」；9歲的林芷晞則說「老師叫我們來」，是前來慶祝香回歸20周年，她又指老師向他們分發退熱貼貼在頸上，以防中暑。Emily覺得老師都頗細心，亦可能是吸取了本月初國家主席習近平訪港後離開時，在赤鱲角機場歡送儀式上有小學生疑因太熱不支倒地的教訓，做足萬全準備。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有市民對解放軍在烈日下暴曬感到「心痛」，紛紛為解放軍撐傘，其中九龍社團聯會成員的陳先生表示，「見到官兵曬到身水身汗好心痛」。他又對於未能領取門票登上「遼寧號」感到遺憾，認為艦隊展示出「國力強大，不再是弱者」。被問到是否知道「遼寧號」駛過時噴出黑煙，陳先生則指中國的艦隊達「國際級」水平，「美國的（航母）肯定更差」，認為市民不會介意。"},{"pid":"ee96ce969dcaea43935714605559a65f31f82329","tid":316860,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170711/s00001/df2334b3a356f70ca4dd9c62a6632b2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2Fdf2334b3a356f70ca4dd9c62a6632b2a.jpg&h=371f7b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170711/s00001/df2850f8e7159dba57ab49f73a086aca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2Fdf2850f8e7159dba57ab49f73a086aca.jpg&h=f7efae78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170711/s00001/df5d0f66a016a58712758b9e00b89e00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2Fdf5d0f66a016a58712758b9e00b89e00.jpg&h=afe87dd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df82ba9db1ad2ac03c485946830ee1d047eb9669","tid":316860,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170711/s00001/1499744271483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2F1499744271483&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c1722439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2F1499744271483&h=4a94d6ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170711/s00001/1499744271483</a>"},{"pid":"21f91f36635ca6410ed586fec15b257189a5dae5","tid":316860,"uid":11001,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"件廢老做乜鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3f7ddab5a3fe52b1e100d7a503bf951fbe0422","tid":316860,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:14:03.000Z","msg":"死廢青少少曬都唔捱得"},{"pid":"53e04dc5a3543e3101bf178a7914cf549e2444dd","tid":316860,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"走啦 好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6378ae5c014b16f5e401c955109f9b5b4e6d27","tid":316860,"uid":37528,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"傘都可以係武器。。。<br />\n解放軍仲唔蚊槍射佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454a5038040e2854f3749dc9dd0d2896e2ae0a32","tid":316860,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T